casebody.data:
Urvashi BHAGAT, petitioner,
v.
Andrei IANCU, Director, United States Patent and Trademark Office. No. 18-277. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 29, 2018.

Motion of Independent Investors, et al. for leave to file out of time a brief as amici curiae denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit denied.
